headline: Will HAE Stock Gain Following Sell-Off of Whole Blood Assets to GVS?
summary: Haemonetics inks a new agreement to sell its whole blood assets to GVS. The transaction is expected to be closed in the first quarter of 2025.

headline: 4 Medical Product Stocks to Buy From a Prospective Industry
summary: An ongoing rise in demand for medical procedures and cost-cutting initiatives should support the Zacks Medical-Products industry. RMD, HAE, PAHC and AGIO are well-poised to gain from the favorable factors.
